Protocol: PhotoFolderDelegation

Types:  
    Agent A,B,P,idp;
    Data photoFolder, Photos;
    Function h, pk;

Knowledge:
    A:   A,B,P,idp,pw(A),pk(idp),photoFolder;
    idp: A,B,P,idp,pw(A),pk(idp),inv(pk(idp));
    P:   A,B,P,idp,pk(idp);
    B:   A,B,P,idp,pk(idp),pk(B),inv(pk(B));

    where A!=B, A!=P, A!=idp, B!=P, B!=idp, P!=idp

Actions:

[A]  *->*  idp : A,idp,pw(A),P,B,photoFolder

idp  *->*  [A] : A,B,photoFolder,{A,B,photoFolder}inv(pk(idp))

[A]  *->*  P   : A,B,photoFolder,{A,B,photoFolder}inv(pk(idp))

P    *->*  B   : P,B,photoFolder,
                 A,B,photoFolder,{A,B,photoFolder}inv(pk(idp))

B    *->*  P   : Photos

Goals:

B authenticates idp on A
Photos secret between B,P